\(\cos\theta=\dfrac{|\mathbf{n}_1\cdot\mathbf{n}_2|}{\|\mathbf{n}_1\|\,\|\mathbf{n}_2\|}
=\dfrac{|2(1)+(-1)(2)+(2)(-1)|}{\sqrt{2^2+(-1)^2+2^2}\sqrt{1^2+2^2+(-1)^2}}
=\dfrac{|-2|}{\sqrt{9}\sqrt{6}}=\dfrac{2}{3\sqrt{6}}=\dfrac{\sqrt{6}}{9}.\) <marks>M1A1</marks>
\(\displaystyle \theta=\arccos\Big(\frac{\sqrt{6}}{9}\Big).\) <marks>A1</marks>
